Reasoning: 
1. cs.CL (Computation and Language) - This paper deals with natural language processing (NLP) and specifically focuses on Chinese pinyin input method engine (IME) which is a subfield of NLP. 
2. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The proposed neural P2C model is a type of artificial intelligence model that uses deep learning techniques to improve the performance of the IME. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The proposed model is a type of machine learning model that uses sequence-to-sequence learning with gated-attention mechanism. 
4. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) - The paper discusses the task of predicting character sequence with incomplete pinyin input, which is related to information retrieval. 
5. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) - The proposed model is a type of neural network model that uses deep learning techniques to improve the performance of the IME.
